     A            C8STNO         3A         COLHDG('LOT #')
     A            C8ISUS        10          COLHDG('ISSUE USER')
     A            C8ISDT         8S 0       COLHDG('ISSUE DATE')
     A            C8ISTM         6S 0       COLHDG('ISSUE TIME')
      *
     A          K C8ISDT
